@startuml FindAllByReadingId

actor User
participant "ReadingQuestionServiceImpl" as RQS
participant "ReadingQuestionRepository" as RQR
participant "ReadingServiceImpl" as RS
participant "BaseServiceImpl" as BSI

== Find All Questions By Reading ID ==
User -> RQS: findAllByReadingId(readingId)
activate RQS

RQS -> RS: isExist(readingId)
activate RS
RS --> RQS: Reading exists
deactivate RS

RQS -> RQR: Find all questions by readingId
activate RQR
RQR --> RQS: List of ReadingQuestion entities
deactivate RQR

loop Convert each entity to DTO
    RQS -> BSI: Call super.convertToDTO(entity)
    note right: convertToDTO được định nghĩa trong BaseServiceImpl\nvà triển khai trong ReadingQuestionServiceImpl
end

RQS --> User: Return list of ReadingQuestionDTO
deactivate RQS

@enduml
